      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/57/1142",
      "text": [
        " اَلصَّفِّ اَلْأَوَّلِ إِلَى اَلصَّفِّ اَلَّذِي خَلْفَكَ وَ تَمْشِيَ مُنْحَرِفاً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1142 - Imam (as) said:\n\"Complete your rows when you see a gap, and it does not harm you to move back if you find tightness in the first row to the row behind you, walking at an angle.\""
        ]
      }
